data.description: The house sits on a spacious corner lot, providing ample outdoor space for various activities and landscaping possibilities. Entering the house, you are greeted by a welcoming foyer that leads into the open living space. The living room is spacious and filled with natural light, thanks to large windows that showcase the outdoor beauty. The house features three well-appointed bedrooms. The master bedroom includes an en-suite bathroom for added privacy and convenience. The two bedrooms on the other side of the home share the nicely updated bathroom. Laundry room and master bathroom has new flooring. Located in the Haysville School District. Close to parks, shopping centers and schools. Feel free to set up your private showing today!
